    "description": {
      "content": "The Alchemy Transfers API provides access to historical on-chain transfer data across EVM-compatible networks. Developers can query asset transfers by address, block range, and transfer category (ETH, ERC-20, ERC-721, ERC-1155, and internal transfers), enabling wallet activity tracking, portfolio history, and transaction auditing.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Alchemy Support",
